<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="watch-n">watch <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /wɒtʃ/    美 /wɑːtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>注视；监视；观察；值班：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>under close watch
被严密监视着</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was standing there <strong>on watch</strong>.
他正站在那儿值班。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(手) 表：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>wear a watch
戴手表</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="keep-watch-for">keep watch (for)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>注视；监视：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He kept watch for the teacher as the students ran around the room.
当同学们在教室追逐嬉闹的时候，他总是望风，注意看老师来了没有。</p></div></div>